# audit/events/
#
# This directory contains structured audit event YAML files produced by the
# scribe-governance-agent at the conclusion of every governed agent activity.
#
# Each file:
#   - Is named: {ISO-8601-timestamp}-{event-id-prefix}.yaml
#     Example: 2026-06-14T150000Z-550e8400.yaml
#   - Conforms to: framework/schemas/metrics-event.schema.json
#   - Is APPEND-ONLY — never modified or deleted after creation
#   - Is committed to the repository as the durable audit trail
#
# To read audit events, use the metrics-collector skill or query this
# directory directly. See audit/README.md for full documentation.
#
# .gitattributes sets merge=union on audit/events/ to prevent merge conflicts
# on concurrent event writes.
